Q-2   Write a solution that takes an input string and returns it with the correct case for character titles in the book.
-The words and, the, of and in should be lowercase.
-All other words should have the first character as uppercase and the rest lowercase.
-Punctuation and spaces must remain in their original positions.
-Hyphenated words are considered separate words.
Input
Title that you need to correct.
Output
Corrected title.
Constraints
0 < TITLE LENGTH < 40
Example
Input

LORD-Of-The WINGs

Output

Lord-of-the Wings

